# Page SEO & JSON-LD

## `Seo` component usage

- Blog posts: use `forceTitle={post.title}` (no `| SEWWA` suffix).
- Static/list pages: use `title="..."` so `| SEWWA` is appended.
- **Every page must pass a unique `description`.** Falling back to `SITE.description`
  means duplicate meta descriptions across tag/list pages — avoid.

```astro
<!-- ✅ GOOD -->
<Seo slot="seo" title="Blog" description={blogDescription} schema={blogSchema} />

<!-- ❌ BAD — inherits site-wide description -->
<Seo slot="seo" title="Blog" />
```

## Forbidden meta tags

- ❌ `<meta name="image">` — non-standard, remove.
- ✅ `og:image`, `twitter:image`, and their `:alt` variants cover image meta.

## JSON-LD per page type

- **Blog post** → `BlogPosting`: `headline`, `description`, `image`, `url`,
  `mainEntityOfPage`, `datePublished`, `dateModified`, `keywords`,
  `articleSection`, `author`, `publisher` (with `logo`).
- **Blog index** → `Blog`: `name`, `url`, `description`.
- **Tag page** → `CollectionPage`: `name`, `url`, `description`.
- **Homepage** → `Organization` + `WebSite`: `name` = `SITE.title` (not
  `titleDefault`), `url`, `description`.
- **About** → `Organization`: `name`, `url`, `description`, `email`.

## Publisher logo (required for `BlogPosting`)

```ts
publisher: {
    '@type': 'Organization',
    name: SITE.title,
    url: SITE.url,
    logo: {
        '@type': 'ImageObject',
        url: new URL('/sewwa.png', SITE.url).href,
        width: 852,
        height: 223,
    },
}
```

## OG image dimensions

- Emit `og:image:width` / `og:image:height` **only** for the default site image
  (currently 1800×945). Per-post images may have different dimensions and
  mismatched hints break social previews.

## Site constants (`constants.ts`)

- `SITE.title` — short brand (`SEWWA`). Use in JSON-LD `name` fields.
- `SITE.titleDefault` — homepage `<title>`. Broader positioning, not one product.
- `SITE.description` — site-wide fallback (≤ 160 chars). Update when positioning shifts.
